name: v5.8.8
body:
## Changelog
* 55e40ab8cb8b5dae095dc303e5be2a32dc73c4f2: Use doctrine.dbal.connections.default.server_version in addition to doctrine.dbal.server_version (@fabpot)
* c3adf8096de33541c8e1a8461845f15fd76b93ab: Strip 1: from DB version on Docker (@fabpot)
* 868898480a06560c5e85aa6befb3fef73fad8315: Rework database URL precedence (@fabpot)
* 1d49ee9131e11b3021bc956b8579b69a6895525e: Fix Doctrine URL when server_version is referencing an env var (@fabpot)
* 03c431ef80f3fdb83bbf01425def6bc7080e3467: Allow PATCH method over HTTP, fix #428 (@tucksaun)
* cce8ca11b278f19f8f9bc67725b1932c4386a589: Add support for `--all` flag on `server:stop` (@alexandre-daubois)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/symfony-cli/symfony-cli/compare/v5.8.7...v5.8.8
